title: Bowlers
provenance: Collection of Carol B. Brener and Stephen W. Brener
description: Oblong, curved lid and sides, raised c-scroll motifs at slightly protruding and rounded corners, featuring raised decoration of bowler in mid stride, 2 players behind him, swags and flowers above, background of swirl motifs, lid features smaller reserve of 5 bowling pins in a row. Reverse features empty reserve, c-scrolls, swags, flowers and beading on lid. Lid hinged on side. Striker incorporated into decorative c-scroll on bottom.
